Text:
Les Journées Particulières at Les Fontaines Parfumées. Located in Grasse, the perfumery capital, the estate’s garden holds a variety of essences from citrus and flowers to trees and herbs. Plan your visit from October 14th-16th at https://t.co/wi4F212HH5
#JPLVMH https://t.co/ODjCnfrNPC

Les Journées Particulières at Rochambeau. Located on a ranch near Dallas, Texas, this ultra-modern workshop combines #LouisVuitton’s traditional craftsmanship with technical innovation. Plan your visit from October 14th-16th at https://t.co/CnuQQzGDfp
#JPLVMH https://t.co/XMN0rkLdR0

Les Journées Particulières at Atelier Prototypes. In the heart of Paris, expert hands bring designers’ drawings to life, crafting models from leather goods, luggage, and more. Plan your visit to #LouisVuitton’s workshops from October 14th-16th at https://t.co/wIlqGrEya2 
#JPLVMH https://t.co/xHxKnFtM4o

Les Journées Particulières at Abbaye Vendôme. This 11th century building was renovated in 2020, becoming the dedicated site to the crafting of precious leathers. Plan your visit to #LouisVuitton’s workshops from October 14th-16th at https://t.co/Yzb4j6uNgT
#JPLVMH https://t.co/SLRnjyOJOz

Les Journées Particulières at the Manufacture de Souliers. Located in Fiesso d’Artico, #LouisVuitton’s shoe-making savoir-faire is carried out in a beautiful space that features eclectic works of art. Plan your visit from October 14th-16th at https://t.co/GCaELXgA0V
#JPLVMH https://t.co/knGM9J5giJ

Les Journées Particulières at Asnières. Built in the Eiffel style, this is where trunks and boxes are crafted, perpetuating #LouisVuitton’s traditions and craftsmanship of exceptional products. Plan your visit from October 14th-16th at https://t.co/gHWRoV0RxS 
#JPLVMH https://t.co/nFNyiRCWbM

“Mirage”. Created by film directors Jia Zhangke and Wei Shujun, a cinematic prelude to the upcoming Louis Vuitton show portrays themes of childhood and discovery on the edge of the Gobi Desert. Watch the show on Facebook or at https://t.co/XktYuyII4t https://t.co/EL1d9v0mru
The #LVMenSS23 Collection plays with the transition from childhood to adulthood, from naïveté to refinement.
In the sandbox and on the beach, children instinctively build sandcastles: constructs of the imagination that turn dreams into reality. #LVMenSS23
In the eyes of a child, the vastness of sand never poses an impossibility, it invites opportunity. #LVMenSS23
There are as many grains of sand on our planet as there are stars in the galaxy. #LVMenSS23
Chinese dancer Hou Young choreographed the #LVMenSS23 show performance.
The #LVMenSS23 will feature a special dance performance, any guesses who choreographed it?

Text: An ambitious homage. Adapted to reflect a local spirit with an exclusive room dedicated to the Brooklyn Balloon Company by Robert Moy, #LOUIS200 Exhibition in LA showcases the imaginative trunks created by a mosaic of talents to mark the bicentennial of #LouisVuitton’s birth.

“200 TRUNKS, 200 VISIONARIES: THE EXHIBITION” has arrived in Los Angeles. Featuring a façade that refers to the Maison’s first trunk motif, the exhibit celebrates the bicentennial of #LouisVuitton’s founder’s birth. See more about #LOUIS200 at https://t.co/Fl7hvHTsqQ https://t.co/G0UUOpVOT8

#NBA Victory travels in Vuitton. Basketball's top prize is one of many coveted trophies to be protected by a custom-made, handcrafted #LouisVuitton case.

Photo Credit © Louis Vuitton Malletier-Michael Hauptman

#FIFA Victory travels in Vuitton. Soccer’s top prize is one of many coveted trophies to be protected by a custom-made, handcrafted #LouisVuitton case.

Photo Credit © Rodrigo Villalba

In preparation for the curtain to rise. Uncover the stories of iconic artists and the loyal companion that will meet their needs throughout their travels: custom #LouisVuitton trunks. Download the Louis Vuitton App to discover the #LVTheBook experiences at https://t.co/8TuIFjPnMU https://t.co/u7FkONVSJD

A jewelry odyssey. True to the Maison’s pioneering spirit, capacity for innovation and constant desire to explore new territories, the #LouisVuitton Spirit collection brings together concepts held dear by the Maison.
#LVHighJewelry

A multi-dimensional journey. Revealed in five themes, the very essence of #LouisVuitton’s spirit is captured in the boldness, novelty, and singular intensity of the fourth High Jewelry Collection designed by Francesca Amfitheatrof.

The perfect canvas for reinterpretation. This season, #LouisVuitton’s Capucines takes on tonal colorblock accents as well as a new Flower Chain, which combines gold links and enamel Monogram flowers. Discover the campaign starring Olympia of Greece at https://t.co/Pseca4CU6V https://t.co/DUUSaAG0rf

A timeless design. Style icon and Friend of the House Olympia of Greece embodies the femininity and elegance of the Maison’s Capucines. Discover the #LouisVuitton campaign shot in London via https://t.co/XM34KXk8de https://t.co/e8pbhfX5u3

The spirit of travel. In a series of interactive experiences, new tales come to life that pay homage to the artists the Maison has supported from its beginnings. Download the #LouisVuitton App to discover the digital version of #LVTheBook magazine at https://t.co/KxPG55oz2B https://t.co/fjhRqXH5DC

Portrait of Mario Lefranc. Practicing a Métier d’Excellence at #LouisVuitton with unique savoir-faire, the Technical Director of Women’s Ready-to-Wear shares how is driven by passion and having a beautiful goal in mind. See the full interview at https://t.co/eIO6o9V1vt https://t.co/E1MV1cyxRU

Portrait of Cindy Renard. Practicing a Métier d’Excellence at #LouisVuitton with unique savoir-faire, the Model Maker and Prototypist shares her passion and the challenges that encourage her to push the limits of her creativity. See the full interview at https://t.co/KHWU2kE439 https://t.co/f6UVSBFz5V

Distinct graphic language. Designed in the Maison’s workshops in Fiesso d’Artico, nine editions of the Louis Vuitton and Nike “Air Force 1” by Virgil Abloh drop on July 19th. Discover the limited-edtiion #LVandNike sneakers at https://t.co/ko32y5trAh https://t.co/ZJu6iwXkWB

Excellence is found in the details. All nine editions of the new #LouisVuitton and Nike “Air Force 1” by Virgil Abloh sneakers that drop on July 19th. Discover all nine high top and low top #LVandNike editions at https://t.co/QeCBa4IaDs https://t.co/D6EHR9LiCW

An anticipated drop. Fusing the sneaker’s original codes with the insignia of the Maison, nine mid-top and low-top versions of the #LouisVuitton and Nike “Air Force 1” by Virgil Abloh are available on July 19th. Discover the #LVandNike collection at https://t.co/LrHIdYKs8M https://t.co/f8duwNCslG
Core ideologies. #LVMenFW22 commemorates the fundamental philosophies that guided Virgil Abloh’s collections for #LouisVuitton.
Symbolic power. #LVMenFW22 consolidates the themes and messages that run through all of Virgil Abloh’s collections for #LouisVuitton.

Presenting Generation “V”. #LouisVuitton’s new campaign brings together friends, talents and familiar faces in a tribute to Virgil Abloh’s lasting legacy of unity and inclusivity. Discover the #LVMenFW22 campaign at https://t.co/u1UCQyZXxw https://t.co/3IZIrosdzK
Open in Paris. Showcasing a selection of pieces from the Men’s Fall-Winter 2022 Collection, #LouisVuitton’s latest Men’s Temporary Residency is now open on the Champs-Elysées through July 31st.

Cross-cultural exchange. As part of LVMH, #LouisVuitton supports La Fabrique NOMADE, a French association that collaborates with refugees with artisanal backgrounds and helps them find professional opportunities. Learn more about @lafabnomade at https://t.co/mu0TaskxOO https://t.co/22QEAWQBPT

Text: Now open: #LouisVuitton summer pop-ups across the Mediterranean. Visit the Maison’s seasonal stores in some of Europe’s most popular destinations from Italy to Spain, Greece and Turkey. Learn more about the openings at https://t.co/zw3aBZX4iz

Now open in Capri, Italy. Bringing its librarie éphémère project to the famous Piazza Umberto this summer, #LouisVuitton opens a pop-up dedicated exclusively to the Maison’s travel editions and an unprecedented City Guide Capri. Discover more at https://t.co/C5W6y6qIfY

An exploration into the world of #LouisVuitton. The Maison’s latest exhibition in Tokyo brings together a remarkable collection of modern pieces and early twentieth-century trunks, artistic collaborations and iconic leather creations. Learn more about #SeeLV below.

#SuzuHirose, #EbizoIchikawa, #Rola, #Kōki, #Nissy and other guests at the #SeeLV opening in Tokyo. Learn about #LouisVuitton’s latest exhibition that celebrates the Maison’s history at https://t.co/kTtIJmhU4C https://t.co/pATwgt6LVs

Now open in Tokyo. An immersive journey covering over 160 years of #LouisVuitton’s history, the travelling exhibition continues after its inauguration in Wuhan in 2020 with stops in Hangzhou and Dubai. Learn more about #SeeLV taking place now through August 21st.

A new chapter. With LV Diamonds, #LouisVuitton expands and deepens its commitment to sustainable practices both environmentally and socially, while introducing the first-ever blockchain-based digital diamond certificate. Learn more at https://t.co/lgzYm86sV2
#LVFineJewelry https://t.co/CQRzhxbQTT

Emotionally charged. Each piece from #LouisVuitton’s LV Diamonds Collection is an invitation to explore new territories, a promise of never-ending discovery. See more from the new #LVFineJewelry Collection available exclusively in the U.S. and Japan at https://t.co/w3GaEKC8QY https://t.co/M3PEBA5Ed5

Emotion Takes Flight with LV Diamonds. #LouisVuitton’s new #LVFineJewelry Collection celebrates the power of diamonds to mark life’s most meaningful moments. Discover the campaign for the new collection released in the U.S. and Japan at https://t.co/Kz49Rdq7fW https://t.co/h3vNdE1uQu
Delicate details. Perfectly complementing her style, Olympia of Greece showcases the latest #LouisVuitton Capucines bags.

Olympia of Greece and the Capucines. #LouisVuitton presents this season’s editions of the iconic Capucines bag, embodied by the Friend of the House in London. Discover the new campaign at https://t.co/xBpcK8ZmKq https://t.co/foUCAFR0Op

A playful demeanor. While retaining #LouisVuitton’s distinctive signatures, touches of purple, mint green, and orange enliven a selection of men’s leather goods in Taurillon Monogram and Monogram Macassar. #LVMen
A refreshing take. In an array of summery hues, #LouisVuitton introduces new sizes of iconic models, including the Keepall and Christopher backpack in Taurillon Monogram and Monogram Macassar.

Colorful expressions. #LouisVuitton unveils new editions of Taurillon Monogram and Monogram Macassar in a rainbow of hues that refer to Virgil Abloh’s first fashion show for the Maison. Discover the latest pieces in the #LVMen leather goods collection at https://t.co/IOE8N39WtD https://t.co/T1aR6LUrro

Discover a dynamic dance-off with performers, John Boogz, Lil Buck, and Mr. Kriss wearing pieces from Virgil Abloh’s archival collections in the new digital edition of #LVTheBook. Download the LV App to see the full film and more immersive experiences at https://t.co/JudlCWfxXV

Celebratory showdown. Discover a dynamic dance-off with performers wearing pieces from Virgil Abloh's archival collections in the new digital edition of #LVTheBook. Download the #LouisVuitton App to see the full film and more immersive experiences at https://t.co/fOvxIQcidu https://t.co/19jVS7qxgQ

Text: At #LouisVuitton’s ateliers, savoir-faire can be learned, respected and transmitted – and innovation nurtured – by artisans who routinely challenge the image of a traditional workshop. Discover Louis Vuitton Manufactures, the new hardcover book at https://t.co/aO8ws1f9jn https://t.co/DY89ZJeYPM

Imaginative expressions. Designed and produced with meticulous detail in #LouisVuitton’s ateliers in Paris, each season’s collections showcase the expertise of the artisans who create these exceptional garments. 

Photographed by Oliver Pilcher and Harald Gottshalk

An olfactory dream. Dedicated to fine perfumery, historic estate Les Fontaines Parfumées, is home to #LouisVuitton’s fragrance workshop in Grasse, the worldwide capital for the art of perfume for almost five centuries.

Photographed by Oliver Pilcher

Unparalleled creativity. With outstanding craftsmanship and passion for their craft, #LouisVuitton’s master jewelers overcome technical challenges with utmost precision, resulting in the most intricate designs. 

Photographed by Oliver Pilcher

Innovative precision. Allowing the Maison to bring its creative spirit and high-quality craftsmanship to this great art, #LouisVuitton’s watchmaking atelier in Geneva gathers the horological talents and métiers in one site. 

Photographed by Oberto Gilli

A mastery of savoir-faire. At #LouisVuitton’s leatherworking ateliers, skilled craftsman balance artisanal heritage and technical innovation, promoting the expertise of local artisans. 

Photographed by Oliver Pilcher

A reputation for excellence. Carried out by the most skilled artisans, the Maison’s atelier in Asnières near Paris has been the stronghold of #LouisVuitton’s trunk-making heritage for over 160 years. 

Photographed by Oliver Pilcher

Introducing Louis Vuitton Manufactures. Published by Assouline, this exclusive book showcases the Maison’s ateliers and artisans who create #LouisVuitton’s exceptional pieces. Discover the new hardcover book at https://t.co/3fQA0d4YOS

Photographed by Oliver Pilcher https://t.co/sIGOZrcZZi
An anthropological approach. An exploration of Virgil Abloh’s creative freedom, the new #LouisVuitton ‘Daybreak’ collection plays with the Maison’s signature DNA.

An informed philosophy. Raising the question of how people buy and wear clothing, Virgil Abloh designed the #LouisVuitton ‘Daybreak’ collection through an anthropological approach and creative freedom.

Creative freedom. Louis Vuitton’s new ‘Daybreak’ Collection exemplifies Virgil Abloh’s philosophies, while fusing the codes of sportswear and workwear. Explore the #LVMen collection at https://t.co/ptcYsjcth9 https://t.co/pRXiDMENia
An urban attitude. #LouisVuitton’s iconic bags are reinvented this season with new details including playful colorblock contrasts and leather braiding that add a delicate, feminine appeal.

Text: A synonym for movement. Staying true to its original design, the Louis Vuitton Keepall embodies the spirit of modern travel.
A canvas for reinterpretation. From Taïga or Taurillon leather to Damier or Graphite canvas, the Keepall maintains its timeless shape, suppleness, and sophistication.
Nomadic elegance. An icon since its creation in the 1930’s, Louis Vuitton’s Keepall is showcased in the latest campaign. Discover the collection at https://t.co/W3mp7pNc27 https://t.co/DjgFIOG5w9

Rooted in heritage. Delicately set in custom-made square baskets that take on the form of the iconic trunk, each of La Mini Malle’s LV Monogram Star-cut diamonds resonate with #LouisVuitton’s engineering genius.
#LVHighJewelry

Timeless signatures. Requiring over 1,200 hours to craft Le Magnétisme necklace, the trunk’s inspiration is visible in the details, echoing the studs and silhouette of #LouisVuitton’s iconic luggage.
#LVHighJewelry

A feast of vibrant hues. In a showcase of unparalleled savoir-faire, Le Multipin necklace reinterprets the hardware of #LouisVuitton’s signature lock, celebrating #LouisVuitton’s creative genius.
#LVHighJewelry

An unparalleled vision. Through immersive and interactive digital experiences, #SeeLV allows visitors to delve deep into the world of #LouisVuitton, uncovering all facets of the Maison’s history and creations through a contemporary lens.

More than 160 years of innovation. #LouisVuitton’s latest exhibition in Dubai mixes archival trunks from the Maison’s heritage collection with recent creations, artistic collaborations and iconic leather designs. Learn more about #SeeLV at https://t.co/DAydJkajLO https://t.co/gxBHvqF2Cu

Now open in Dubai. An immersive journey covering over 160 years of #LouisVuitton’s history, the travelling exhibition continues after its first two stops in Wuhan in 2020 and Hangzhou in 2021. Learn more about #SeeLV taking place through March 7th at https://t.co/KqktWhua30 https://t.co/FCGBDEyzJq
